2
00:00:02,240 --> 00:00:04,820
Today we're going to be looking at one of the biggest genres of games.

3
00:00:04,820 --> 00:00:09,420
The games many players associate with family and friends, games that have been making a comeback in recent years.

4
00:00:09,420 --> 00:00:11,260
We're talking about board games.

5
00:00:11,260 --> 00:00:18,680
Now, there are tons of board games out there, but we're going to take a slightly different approach today and look really closely at just two board games that define their eras.

6
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:23,140
The family classic, Monopoly, and the game that brought Euro Games to the US, Settlers of Catan.

7
00:00:23,140 --> 00:00:26,980
And we'll try to touch on how their history and reception have helped define the genre.

8
00:00:26,980 --> 00:00:36,140
